            . The prisoner came to my house, on the Sunday before the 23d of December, and asked if I wanted a pair of scales, and if I would go to a person who had them to sell, I might have them cheap - I did not go; but on the 23d of December, he brought these scales and weights, and left them; and soon after the prosecutor called for them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340102-81-person650">
                  JOHN 
