            . I am an officer - I took the prisoner in bed - he said the woman ordered him to sell them.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going by with my milk on the 23rd of December - the prosecutrix called me in, and said she was half-a-year's rent in debt, and she was about to let her shop to a man who was to give her Â£12 for the fixtures and good will, but he declined to do so; and she asked me to inquire if I could sell the things; and I took them to Mrs. Laws, and left them for her to make the best bargain she could for them.</p>
